name: clearScreen
desc: Clears entire screen and moves cursor to upper left.

desc: Closing tag for Erase in Display (Clear Screen).

name: clearScreenOpen

desc: Clears entire screen and delete all lines saved in the scrollback buffer.

desc: Returns the current cursor position if possible.
